    Janus                       151472 0.165 0.007  0.6945   14.4      196×192×150 0.656±.094 0.6        1966 Audouin Dollfus        2.01  0.0523      S
    Mimas                       185520 1.566 0.0202 0.942422 12.8      397.2 ± 1.2 1.165±.023 0.6        1789 William Herschel      38.0   0.161       S
    Enceladus                   238020 0.010 0.0004 1.370218 11.8      498.8 ± 0.4 1.603±0345 0.99       1789 William Herschel      84.0   0.212       S
    Telesto                     294700 1.158 0.001  1.887802 18.5      34×28×26    1.0        1.0        1980 B. Smith                                 S
    Tethys                      294700 0.168 0.000  1.887802 10.2      1059.8 ± 3  0.991±.009 0.9        1684 Giovanni Cassini     755     0.436       S
    Calypso                     294700 1.473 0.001  1.887802 18.7      34×22×22    1.0        0.7        1980 B. Smith                                 S
    Dione                       377400 0.002 0.0022 2.736915 10.4      1118 ± 10   1.490±.040 0.7        1684 Giovanni Cassini    1050     0.500       S
    Helene                      377400 0.212 0.005  2.736915 18.4      36×32×30    1.5        0.6        1980 Laques-Lecacheus                         S
    @{i}End of Outermost Ring@{ui} (E)   480000
    Rhea                        527040 0.327 0.0010 4.517500  9.6      1528 ± 8    1.240±.044 0.7        1672 Giovanni Cassini    2490     0.659       S
    Titan                      1221850 1.634 0.0292 15.94542  8.4      5150 ± 2    1.881±.005 0.21       1655 Christian Huygens 135000     2.65        S
